		<news>
[B]Update - v6.7.78 - Jun 12th, 2026 [/B]
--[Fix] Real-Debrid resolve timeout increased (configurable, default 30s) to prevent skipping uncached sources.
--[Fix] Largest-file fallback when movie filename matching fails.
--[Fix] Multi-source playback fallback; fixed errorForSources crash when auto-retry is enabled.
--[Fix] Playlist cleared during resolve to reduce Kodi skipping unplayable plugin URLs.
--[Change] Added Real-Debrid resolve timeout setting.
--[Fix] Relaxed extras filter (removed overly broad feature keyword).
[B]Update - v6.7.77 - May 26th, 2026 [/B]
--[Fix] Small fix pushed for blank My TV Shows and My Movies menus.
--[Change] Made Main menu, Movies, TV Shows, My Movies, and My TV Shows all dynamic menus that can be enabled, disabled, re-ordered, or custom shortcuts can be added.
--[Change] Added option to prefer smaller file sizes in source select.
--[Fix] Change made to prevent multiple threads when resolving rd from causing users to get rate limited. Threading using semaphore limit of 3.
--[Fix] Downloads now pad single digits with a leading zero on folder name and file name.
--[Change] Change to cloud scrapers to reduce number of false matches.
--[Fix] Changes made for season pack on torbox when downloading being named file-hash instead of source file name.
--[Fix] Changes made for local tracking and marking movies.
--[Change] Change made so that dropping a show on trakt immediately updates.
--[Change] Added a new setting to filter known infringing filenames from rd. Setting added to rd section in settings.
--[Change] Added Finish Watching for MDBList for movies and shows. (if you do not want it, just hide it)
--[Change] Added the ability to browse addons for shortcut creation.
--[Change] Added the ability to select icons from skin, umbrella, or custom url when setting a custom shortcut.
--[Change] Added shortcut folders. The option is under Tools.
--[Change] Added ability to edit custom items. Label, icon, or path.
--[Change] Added ability to use kodi built in functions as custom items. (Reload Skin or Exit Kodi)
--[Fix] Change made for plex authorization.
		</news>
